<refsect1 id="SO-S-29a">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>
  This example demonstrates how to implement Yahoo Maps API Generated Rss feed.</para>
  <para>For more information on Yahoo Maps API visit: 
  <ulink url="http://developer.yahoo.net/maps/simple/index.html">http://developer.yahoo.net/maps/simple/index.html</ulink>
  </para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1 id="SO-S-29b">
  <title>Breakdown</title>
  <para>Yahoo Maps API can get map information using data formatted in Web-standard RSS format. 
  We show in 'yahoomaps.vsp' how you can easily generated the feed to be posted to yahoo using just 
  one SQL statement with xml_auto function. For more information on xml_auto refer to the documentation.
  </para>
</refsect1>

